docs.lead_paragraph: PLATTSBURG, N.Y., July 30 -- George T. Weed, who was appointed Collector or the Port of Plattsburg yesterday, is a son of Smith M. Weed, and for a number of years he has been prominent in Northern New-York politics.

headline.main: COLLECTOR G.T. WEED'S CAREER.; Has Held Important Trusts, and His District Pleased with the Appointment.
